{"tid":1591002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒漩渦已經慢慢形成緊","createTime":"2019-09-24T03:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T07:21:58.000Z","uid":61886,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"693354fe66b93cd8b47442864ef2f70eeb6ddd95","tid":1591002,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:36:24.000Z","msg":"【逆權運動】來港航線入不敷支　國泰港航籲政府豁免機場著陸停泊費<br />\n<br />\n國泰本月公佈8月份客、貨運量數據，當月來港載客量較去年同期顯著減少38%，離港客運量則減少12%。8月總載客量按年跌逾一成，是公司自2018年10月以來首次錄得下跌。另一方面，上周香港航空亦披露，由於香港持續發生事件，令旅遊需求大幅下降。因應市況，已暫時調低9月至12月的運力達9%，航班數量亦會下調7%。根據8月機場載客量數據顯示，香港機場載客量按年大跌12.4%或減少至少85萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190923&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60075223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190923%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60075223&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=77b3997d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190923%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60075223&h=6686ba76\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190923&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60075223</a><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n金管局急晤業界　商延期還款吊命<br />\n<br />\n反修例風波自今年六月爆發至今仍未平息，令訪港旅客量按年急跌近一半，不少與旅遊業唇齒相依行業，如零售、酒店及餐飲自然首當其衝，生意額直線插水，連累從業員收入大減，甚至要放無薪假，以減低營運成本。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190924/mobile/bkn-20190924033042065-0924_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190924%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190924033042065-0924_00822_001.html&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=8b806f9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190924/mobile/bkn-20190924033042065-0924_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而家係一場多方向既戰爭<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好太拘泥於一場戰役嘅勝負同成效<br />\n<br />\n日常化嘅遊行示威只會令漩渦越滾越大<br />\n<br />\n直至去到一發不可收拾為止<br />\n<br />\n加上美國戰線<br />\n<br />\n一齊擁抱大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLet's burn together <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"caa5464cf6db5d54afd738bb34df8b3991ef9a50","tid":1591002,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b255de7a1a5732b704c311ccf8c69c52409c89c","tid":1591002,"uid":293698,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:37:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80911678694b59156becfaa5bb9a3b08b05dc1cf","tid":1591002,"uid":276150,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:38:56.000Z","msg":"已經形成咗㗎喇！依家結果慢慢浮現<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a391349f8f6411dd52d44085f30cf904d17b3d2","tid":1591002,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:41:03.000Z","msg":"If, we burn, you with us<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0351afcda56a5fe35717646d3555dd5211ee0423","tid":1591002,"uid":10070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:51:39.000Z","msg":"我要攬炒"},{"pid":"316e9379ba2b70e450c3598c6da702ff90fd40e3","tid":1591002,"uid":214173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:52:55.000Z","msg":"蝴蝶效應續漸浮現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19883a1a87ea83bb9d6586cd136b5c43b9e17654","tid":1591002,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7f4cebdcd08d4f2acee96ca1d55130c2bd52f3","tid":1591002,"uid":193215,"like":1,"dislike":